Project.How do you plan to prepare the dataset:
Take nrel-pds-wtk/seasiawind_v2 as an example, each file size is 130.1GB,

We first use AWS's s3 tool to download all the data, and then split each large file into about 17G in size;
Make it into a car file and put the splitting method in the index file; so that the downloader can find the combination method of the original file;
Files in other directories are also processed in the same way.
